OL,3,CEmma Raducanu proud despite final
OL,4,Cdefeat at Queen's Club
OL,6,FEmma Raducanu said she was eager to
OL,7,Fdraw a silver lining after coming
OL,8,Fagonisingly short of a fairytale
OL,9,Fending at the HSBC Championships with
OL,10,Fa 6-0 7-6 (6) loss to Donna Vekic in
OL,11,Fthe final.
OL,13,FThe British number one, who powered
OL,14,Fthrough a two-match Saturday to reach
OL,15,FSunday's showdown, was swiftly beaten
OL,16,Fin a 28-minute first set, but battled
OL,17,Fthe Croatian to the brink of a
OL,18,Fgripping second, saving four match
OL,19,Fpoints, including one in the tie-break.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
