OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781635704
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu proud despite final
OL,4,Cdefeat at Queen's Club
OL,6,FIt was the 23-year-old's first tour-
OL,7,Flevel final on grass, and her third
OL,8,Fsince winning the US Open in 2021.
OL,10,F"It was tough to take, for sure, but I
OL,11,Fhad a good week here, and it was just
OL,12,Famazing to play at home," said
OL,13,FRaducanu, who, as a result of rain
OL,14,Fdelays and postponements earlier in
OL,15,Fthe week, had spent two hours and 19
OL,16,Fminutes more on court the previous day
OL,17,Fthan her opponent.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
