OL,3,CEmma Raducanu proud despite final
OL,4,Cdefeat at Queen's Club
OL,6,FRaducanu slipped in the first of those
OL,7,Fmatches and, as she had for her semi-
OL,8,Ffinal victory over American Iva Jovic,
OL,9,Femerged on court wearing significant
OL,10,Fstrapping on the inside of her left
OL,11,Fthigh, which she removed late in the
OL,12,Ffirst set.
OL,14,FShe said: "I have just been dealing
OL,15,Fwith a few niggles over the past few
OL,16,Fweeks, and of course the load I have
OL,17,Fhad in the last week, it's been a
OL,18,Fgreat problem to have, you know,
OL,19,Fplaying this many matches. And
OL,20,Fdoubling up (on Saturday), it's not
OL,21,Feasy to recover from.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
