CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781635704
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu proud despite final
OL,4,Cdefeat at Queen's Club
OL,6,F"Grass, these things can happen. You
OL,7,Ftake a few slips. But I think overall
OL,8,FI came through a challenging day (on
OL,9,FSaturday). I put myself in this
OL,10,Fposition to be in the final.
OL,12,F"The crowd were amazing. It meant a
OL,13,Flot to have the support all week."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
