OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781635704
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu proud despite final
OL,4,Cdefeat at Queen's Club
OL,6,FThose who stuck around to watch the
OL,7,Ffinal match at the Andy Murray Arena
OL,8,Fgot to witness British joy after
OL,9,FOlivia Nicholls and Slovak partner
OL,10,FTereza Mihalikova won the doubles
OL,11,Ftournament, beating Canadian-German
OL,12,Fpair Leylah Fernandez and Laura
OL,13,FSiegemund 6-3 6-7 (4) 10/7.
OL,15,FRaducanu in May reunited with Andrew
OL,16,FRichardson, the coach who guided her
OL,17,Fto that famous US Open triumph as a
OL,18,Fqualifier, and did not drop a set at
OL,19,FQueen's until the first in the final.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
