OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781635704
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu proud despite final
OL,4,Cdefeat at Queen's Club
OL,6,FThis very encouraging run for
OL,7,FRaducanu, after years under what has
OL,8,Foften seemed like crushing
OL,9,Fexpectation, was not, she insisted on
OL,10,FSaturday, a return to her former self,
OL,11,Fbut the incarnation of a "new Emma".
OL,13,FThat has meant a mental reset as much
OL,14,Fas a physical one, and resilient
OL,15,FRaducanu refused to make it easy for
OL,16,FVekic, who overturned a 5-2 deficit in
OL,17,Fthe second set and saved two set
OL,18,Fpoints in the 10th game.
OL,26,@sD@ZOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
