OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781635704
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu proud despite final
OL,4,Cdefeat at Queen's Club
OL,6,FDespite twice failing to force a
OL,7,Fdecider, Raducanu pushed on, digging
OL,8,Fdeep to save a trio of championship
OL,9,Fpoints to make it 6-6 to set up the
OL,10,Ftie-break, then fended off another one
OL,11,Fbefore hitting out at the end of the
OL,12,Ffinal rally.
OL,14,FShe added: "The performances I had
OL,15,Fthis week, I played really well. I was
OL,16,Fable to play and dictate, and that's
OL,17,Fsomething I wasn't able to do (in the
OL,18,Ffinal).
OL,26,@vD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
