CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781635704
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu proud despite final
OL,4,Cdefeat at Queen's Club
OL,6,F"I managed to get myself back into the
OL,7,Fsecond set, and I'm proud of how I
OL,8,Ffought. That's not something that in
OL,9,Fthe past years I have always done, so
OL,10,Fthat's a positive."
